Class Flak

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.GamePlayObjects.Flak

    Building, Defensive, GamePlayObject, Unit

    public class Flak
extends java.lang.Object
implements GamePlayObject, Defensive, Building, Unit
    The Server Side Class Tank. Range is the Range in which the Tank can Attack. movingRange is the Range the Tank can move in one Phase.
